critical_positive: The gentleman was very easy to talk to and friendly. He was interesting because he was from a different section of the country and extensively well read and traveled so I could learn from him. critical_negative: I think the only thing that might not have worked well was that we spoke over each other once in a while. But really, that happens in every day conversations. critical_positive: Everything worked as it should have. We didn't have any technical issues and we found common things to talk about. We both have some of the same interests which was helpful. critical_negative: It took a little time to find common ground. I have traveled a ton and she had not so it was kind of difficult to find things in common at first. Once we found a few things we had in common it was just fine. The initial figuring out what to talk about was the only real thing we had to overcome.
